pullrequest.title: Modeling of simspark NAO robot and its Controller

content.raw: But these binaries are compiled for a particular distribution (Ubuntu Trusty for example). If I have a different version of the libraries it's not going to work. Is there any way to spawn the model via the Gazebo UI without any plugin just for checking the model?
